hospital-game-engine-corsixth-v067-gets-a-first-beta/</guid></item><item><title>Steam Deck 与 Starfield 的兼容性将在“稍后”讨论</title><link>https://www.gamingonlinux.com/2023/06/steam-deck-compatibility-with-starfield-to-be-discussed-later-down-the-road/</link><description>《Starfield》将于 9 月 6 日发布，显然有很多令人兴奋的事情，但它会在 Valve 的 Steam Deck 上运行吗？目前尚不清楚。</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Jun 2023 13:17:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.gamingonlinux.com/2023/06/steam-deck-compatibility-with-starfield-to-be-discussed-later-down-the-road/</guid></item><item><title>Valve 聘请了另一家 Linux 游戏图形驱动程序开发商</title><link>https://www.gamingonlinux.com/2023/06/valve-pulls-in-another-graphics-driver-developer-for-linux-gaming/</link><description>Valve 显然对 Linux 游戏和 Steam Deck 仍然抱有很大的野心，最近事实证明，他们又聘请了另一位开发人员来开发开源图形驱动程序。</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Jun 2023 13:00:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.gamingonlinux.com/2023/06/valve-pulls-in-another-graphics-driver-developer-for-linux-gaming/</guid></item><item><title>开源 NVIDIA NVK 驱动程序进展顺利</title><link>https://www.gamingonlinux.com/2023/06/the-open-source-nvidia-nvk-driver-is-coming-along-well/</link><description>我非常关注的一个项目是 NVK，这是由社区（而不是 NVIDIA）开发的开源 NVIDIA Vulkan 驱动程序，而且看起来它的进展相当顺利。</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Jun 2023 09:13:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.gamingonlinux.com/2023/06/the-open-source-nvidia-nvk-driver-is-coming-along-well/</guid></item><item><title>Steam Deck 拥有超过 10,000 款经过验证且可玩的游戏</title><link>https://www.gamingonlinux.com/2023/06/steam-deck-hits-over-10000-verified-and-playable-games/</link><description>Steam Deck 刚刚达到了一个重要里程碑，目前有超过 10,000 款游戏被评为“已验证”或“可玩”。</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Jun 2023 08:55:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.gamingonlinux.com/2023/06/steam-deck-hits-over-10000-verified-and-playable-games/</guid></item><item><title>在 2023 年 GOG 夏季特卖中免费获得 RPG 卡牌战斗游戏《Ancient Enemy》的副本</title><link>https://www.gamingonlinux.com/2023/06/free-rpg-card-battler-ancient-enemy-gog-summer-sale-2023/</link><description>准备好玩另一款免费游戏了吗？是的，另一个！ 《Ancient Enemy》是 GOG 上的最新赠品，它应该可以在带有 Wine / Proton 的 Linux 上正常运行。</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Jun 2023 13:48:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.gamingonlinux.com/2023/06/free-rpg-card-battler-ancient-enemy-gog-summer-sale-2023/</guid></item><item><title>自上而下的折纸益智冒险 Paper Trail 谈及 Steam Deck 支持</title><link>https://www.gamingonlinux.com/2023/06/top-down-paper-folding-puzzle-adventure-paper-trail-talks-up-steam-deck-support/</link><description>需要为您的 Steam Deck 或 Proton 桌面 Linux 提供更多游戏吗？ Paper Trail 看起来非常可爱，开发者显然是 Steam Deck 的忠实粉丝。</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Jun 2023 13:26:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.gamingonlinux.com/2023/06/top-down-paper-folding-puzzle-adventure-paper-trail-talks-up-steam-deck-support/</guid></item><item><title>国王战役发布后即可在 Steam Deck 和 Linux 桌面上玩</title><link>https://www.gamingonlinux.com/2023/06/the-kings-campaign-will-be-playable-on-steam-deck-and-linux-desktop-at-release/</link><description>Reverie World Studios 和 Bad Logic Studios 的《国王战役》将于 7 月 13 日发布，他们最近在 Steam Deck 上进行了详细的改进工作。</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Jun 2023 13:18:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.gamingonlinux.com/2023/06/the-kings-campaign-will-be-playable-on-steam-deck-and-linux-desktop-at-release/</guid></item></channel></rss>